retrieval.storage.index.patchs

Interface PicturePatchsIndex

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    KyotoCabinetPatchsIndexSingleFile, SimpleHashMapPatchsIndex

    public interface PicturePatchsIndex
    This interface allow to implement methods for a Picture Patchs Index This index must map image id with their number of patchs ex: [48-500;49-1000] image 48 has 500 patchs and 49 has 1000 patchs in index
